desc: Beginning Film is a collection of vintage film camera and accessories sourced from Tokyo, Japan and based in Sydney, Australia. We source a range of film cameras from Point and Shoots, SLR, Medium Format to 35mm Film and brands from Canon, Mamiya, Contax, Olympus, Pentax, Minolta, Kyocera, Konica and many more!
